episodes.title: Episode 45: Why Are Ex-Jehovah's Witnesses So Angry?
episodes.description:
www.whatsupwatchtower.com
Twitter: @UpWatchtower
Facebook: www.facebook.com/whatsupwatchtower

Hello Everyone, this is our first official "rant" video which we have divided into two parts.  We just wanted to air out some thoughts we've been having in conjunction with recent headlines in the United States along with news in the Ex-Jehovah's Witness community.  Our language is a little more forceful than you are probably used to us using, but we feel very passionately about what we are doing and the importance of this moment in history, especially as it relates to the future of the Jehovah's Witness organization.
